Description.Text: A fantastic top quality product with a very central location. (11/06 MW)
The hotel is located in the very heart of Moscow, only a few steps away from the Red Square and the Bolshoy Theatre.

The rooms are large and are of very high standard. The rooms are furnished with Italian furniture and are designed and decorated by Italian architects and designers. Rooms are equipped with all modern facilities and are in excellent condition.
The building has a beautiful classical facade.
The Savoy restaurant has a rich history. It has been renovated completely and has a unique interior of Rococo style.

The lobby is large and impressive. A large reception and concierge desk is located in the corner. Opposite is a comfortable seating area with beautiful antique furniture. Further down is the cosy modern lobby bar.
